com/news/music/watch-the-zombies-colin-blunstone-join-finneas-for-time-of-the-season-duet-3844805">观看僵尸的Colin Blunstone加入Finneas的“本赛季时间”二重奏</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
