即将来临</a>。</p><p>在当晚，Jade还让人们谈论她的红地毯外观 - 穿着完整的婚纱参加活动，并由她的“音乐经理丈夫”加入。这是在“我梦dream以求的天使”音乐录影带中统治她的可怕的行业执行人物。</p><p> In other JADE news, at the end of the year, &#39;Angel Of My Dreams&#39; landed at Number Five on <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024-3817596"><em>NME&#39;</em> s 50 best songs of 2024 list</a> , and the debut solo single was described as “absolutely riveting”.</p><p> Since then, the singer has <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-mix-jade-completes-all-female-headliners-at-mighty-hoopla-2025-3830418">been announced as the third female headliner for this year&#39;s Mighty Hoopla festival</a> in London. She joins the bill alongside <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kesha">Kesha</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ciara">Ciara</a> , who <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-and-ciara-to-play-uk-festival-exclusive-shows-at-mighty-hoopla-2025-3805266">were confirmed last October</a> . <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fjade-tickets%2Fartist%2F2168500" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit here</a> for remaining tickets.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jade-shares-tmz-parody-article-teaser-for-her-upcoming-single-fufn-fuck-you-for-now-3844757">JADE shares TMZ-parody article teaser for her upcoming single &#39;FUFN (Fuck You For Now)&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
